<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">وَصَحَّ عَنْ حَفْصَةَ رَضِيَ اللهُ عَنْهَا:</span> <span class="c2">«أَنَّهَا أَمَرَتْ بِقَتْلِ جَارِيَةٍ لَهَا سَحَرَتْهَا؛ فَقُتِلَتْ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَكَذَلِكَ:</span> صَحَّ عَنْ جُنْدُبٍ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ أَحْمَدُ:</span> <span class="c2">«عَنْ ثَلَاثَةٍ مِنْ أَصْحَابِ النَّبِيِّ صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>* * *<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>